_sText:
A long time ago I played the map on TF2. I looked everywhere and I could not find the CSS version. This lead to me with the help of rvrb to bring the map back into CSS with edits and optimization, as a lot has deteriorated since then.

The map was presumably played in Commonwealth Gaming during, 2012-2013? The branding is Burning Baby Productions. I knew Theodore made the TF2 map, so I asked them if they had the CSS map file. They didn't, but have a decompiled vmf of a decompiled CSS version from 6/23/2013, This was the base to work on.
